#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn4.22"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.22:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.22:0.2"
msgid "3. Tatiyavagga "
msgstr "3. Māra "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn4.22:0.3"
msgid "22. Samiddhisutta "
msgstr "22. With Samiddhi "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.119, pts2ed1.263, sc1
msgctxt "sn4.22:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati silāvatiyaṃ. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Sakyans near Silāvatī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.22:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā samiddhi bhagavato avidūre appamatto ātāpī pahitatto viharati. "
msgstr "Now at that time Venerable Samiddhi was meditating not far from the Buddha, diligent, keen, and resolute. "

msgctxt "sn4.22:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato samiddhissa rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi: "
msgstr "Then as Venerable Samiddhi was in private retreat this thought came to his mind, "

msgctxt "sn4.22:1.4"
msgid "“lābhā vata me, suladdhaṃ vata me, "
msgstr "“I’m so fortunate, so very fortunate, "

msgctxt "sn4.22:1.5"
msgid "yassa me satthā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho. "
msgstr "to have a teacher who is a perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha! "

msgctxt "sn4.22:1.6"
msgid "Lābhā vata me, suladdhaṃ vata me, "
msgstr "I’m so fortunate, so very fortunate, "

msgctxt "sn4.22:1.7"
msgid "yvāhaṃ evaṃ svākkhāte dhammavinaye pabbajito. "
msgstr "to have gone forth in a teaching and training so well explained! "

msgctxt "sn4.22:1.8"
msgid "Lābhā vata me, suladdhaṃ vata me, "
msgstr "I’m so fortunate, so very fortunate, "

msgctxt "sn4.22:1.9"
msgid "yassa me sabrahmacārino sīlavanto kalyāṇadhammā”ti. "
msgstr "to have spiritual companions who are ethical and of good character.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.22:1.10"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā āyasmato samiddhissa cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya yenāyasmā samiddhi tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmato samiddhissa avidūre mahantaṃ bhayabheravaṃ saddamakāsi, apissudaṃ pathavī maññe undrīyati. "
msgstr "And then Māra the Wicked, knowing what Samiddhi was thinking, went up to him and made a terrifyingly loud noise close by him. It seemed as if the earth was shattering. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn4.22:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā samiddhi yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno āyasmā samiddhi bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Samiddhi went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and told him what had happened. The Buddha said, "

msgctxt "sn4.22:2.2"
msgid "“idhāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavato avidūre appamatto ātāpī pahitatto viharāmi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn4.22:2.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn4.22:2.4"
msgid "‘lābhā vata me, suladdhaṃ vata me, "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn4.22:2.5"
msgid "yassa me satthā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn4.22:2.6"
msgid "Lābhā vata me, suladdhaṃ vata me, "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn4.22:2.7"
msgid "yvāhaṃ evaṃ svākkhāte dhammavinaye pabbajito. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn4.22:2.8"
msgid "Lābhā vata me, suladdhaṃ vata me, "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn4.22:2.9"
msgid "yassa me sabrahmacārino sīlavanto kalyāṇadhammā’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn4.22:2.10"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, avidūre mahābhayabheravasaddo ahosi, apissudaṃ pathavī maññe undrīyatī”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. REF: pts1ed1.120, pts2ed1.264, sc3
msgctxt "sn4.22:3.1"
msgid "“Nesā, samiddhi, pathavī undrīyati. "
msgstr "“Samiddhi, that’s not the earth shattering. "

msgctxt "sn4.22:3.2"
msgid "Māro eso pāpimā tuyhaṃ vicakkhukammāya āgato. "
msgstr "That’s Māra the Wicked come to pull the wool over your eyes! "

msgctxt "sn4.22:3.3"
msgid "Gaccha tvaṃ, samiddhi, tattheva appamatto ātāpī pahitatto viharāhī”ti. "
msgstr "Go back to that same place, Samiddhi, and meditate, diligent, keen, and resolute.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.22:3.4"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho āyasmā samiddhi bhagavato paṭissutvā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” replied Samiddhi. He got up from his seat, bowed, and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on his right, before leaving. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.22:3.5"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho āyasmā samiddhi tattheva appamatto ātāpī pahitatto vihāsi. "
msgstr "And for a second time Samiddhi was meditating in that same place, diligent, ardent, and resolute. "

msgctxt "sn4.22:3.6"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho āyasmato samiddhissa rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa … pe … "
msgstr "And for a second time he had the same thought … "

msgctxt "sn4.22:3.7"
msgid "dutiyampi kho māro pāpimā āyasmato samiddhissa cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya … pe … "
msgstr "and Māra made an earth-shattering noise. "

msgctxt "sn4.22:3.8"
msgid "apissudaṃ pathavī maññe undrīyati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.22:3.9"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā samiddhi māraṃ pāpimantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Samiddhi addressed Māra the Wicked One in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn4.22:4.1"
msgid "“Saddhāyāhaṃ pabbajito, "
msgstr "“I went forth out of faith "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.22:4.2"
msgid "agārasmā anagāriyaṃ; "
msgstr "from the lay life to homelessness. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.22:4.3"
msgid "Sati paññā ca me buddhā, "
msgstr "My mindfulness and wisdom are mature, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.22:4.4"
msgid "cittañca susamāhitaṃ; "
msgstr "my mind is serene in immersion. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.22:4.5"
msgid "Kāmaṃ karassu rūpāni, "
msgstr "Make whatever illusions you want, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.22:4.6"
msgid "neva maṃ byādhayissasī”ti. "
msgstr "it won’t bother me.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn4.22:5.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ samiddhi bhikkhū”ti dukkhī dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The mendicant Samiddhi knows me!” miserable and sad, vanished right there."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
